Trinity::

She smiled at Scat as Aerotaur put him down on the ground. "See? we 
only want you to be our friend. We all look out for eachother here. 
It's kind of like a family. So, now your part of the family. And 
family doesn't hurt family." She walked over to Scat and looked up at 
him."Want something to eat? I can get you some energon if you want?"
